            <p>Individually, students write a journal entry about the number line. What is it? What are the rules? Make a number line that you would use to show <abbr title="two eighths"><sup>2</sup>/<sub>8</sub></abbr>. Could you use this number line to show <abbr title="two fifths"><sup>2</sup>/<sub>5</sub></abbr>? Pairs share their journal entries.</p>
